## Authentication and Authorization

**Admin URL:** `https://admin.youorder.me`

Admin uses separate authentication from B2B.

```typescript
// Admin login credentials (from .env)
ADMIN_EMAIL=admin@client.com
ADMIN_PASSWORD=${ADMIN_PASSWORD}

// Admin login flow
test('should login to admin', async ({ page }) => {
  await page.goto('https://admin.youorder.me/auth/login');
  await page.fill('input[name="email"]', process.env.ADMIN_EMAIL!);
  await page.fill('input[name="password"]', process.env.ADMIN_PASSWORD!);
  await page.click('button[type="submit"]');
  await expect(page).toHaveURL(/\/dashboard/);
});
```

### Role Validation (Critical)

Admin must enforce role-based access control:

```typescript
test('should deny access to commerce role token', async ({ page }) => {
  // Login as commerce user (B2B credentials)
  await loginAsCommerce(page);
  // Try to access admin
  await page.goto('https://admin.youorder.me/dashboard');
  // Should redirect to login or show 403
  await expect(page).not.toHaveURL(/\/dashboard/);
});

test('should deny unauthenticated access', async ({ page }) => {
  await page.goto('https://admin.youorder.me/dashboard');
  await expect(page).toHaveURL(/\/auth\/login/);
});
```

## Key Admin Flows

### Order Management

Test case IDs follow `ADM-ORD-{NN}` pattern.

| Scenario | What to Validate |
|----------|-----------------|
| View orders list | Orders visible, filterable by status/date |
| View order detail | Items, amounts, commerce info, ERP status |
| Update order status | Status change reflected in B2B and APP |
| Filter orders by client | Multi-tenant isolation (admin sees own client's orders) |
| Export orders CSV | File downloads, data is correct |

### Store Configuration

Configuration changes in Admin affect what B2B users see. This is the highest-risk area.

```typescript
test('should save anonymous access setting', async ({ page }) => {
  await adminLogin(page);
  await page.goto('/settings/store');

  const toggle = page.locator('[data-testid="anonymous-access-toggle"]');
  await toggle.click();
  await page.locator('button:has-text("Guardar")').click();

  await expect(page.locator('.success-toast')).toBeVisible();

  // Verify reflected in B2B
  const b2bPage = await context.newPage();
  await b2bPage.goto(`https://${client.slug}.youorder.me/products`);
  // If anonymous access enabled, should not redirect to login
  await expect(b2bPage).not.toHaveURL(/\/auth\/login/);
});
```

### Banner Management

| Scenario | What to Validate |
|----------|-----------------|
| Create banner with image | Banner saves, preview correct |
| Set banner URL | Link navigates to correct destination |
| Activate/deactivate banner | Visible/invisible in B2B |
| Set banner date range | Shows only in configured period |

### Promotion Management

| Scenario | What to Validate |
|----------|-----------------|
| Create catalog promotion | Promotion visible in B2B (discounted price shows) |
| Edit promotion percentage | Price reflects new discount |
| Set promotion date range | Starts and ends at configured times |
| Deactivate promotion | Price returns to normal in B2B |

## Spec Template

```typescript
import { test, expect } from '@playwright/test';

const ADMIN_URL = 'https://admin.youorder.me';

test.describe('Admin - {Feature}', () => {
  test.beforeEach(async ({ page }) => {
    await page.goto(`${ADMIN_URL}/auth/login`);
    await page.fill('input[name="email"]', process.env.ADMIN_EMAIL!);
    await page.fill('input[name="password"]', process.env.ADMIN_PASSWORD!);
    await page.click('button[type="submit"]');
    await page.waitForURL(/\/dashboard/);
  });

  test('should {action} {context}', async ({ page }) => {
    // Arrange
    await page.goto(`${ADMIN_URL}/{path}`);

    // Act
    await page.locator('[data-testid="{element}"]').click();

    // Assert
    await expect(page.locator('[data-testid="{result}"]')).toBeVisible();
  });
});
```

## Naming Conventions

**Spec files:** `{feature}.spec.ts`
- `login.spec.ts`
- `orders.spec.ts`
- `stores.spec.ts`

**Test case IDs (checklists):**
- `ADM-ACC-{NN}` — Admin access control
- `ADM-ORD-{NN}` — Admin orders
- `ADM-STR-{NN}` — Admin store config
- `ADM-RPT-{NN}` — Admin reports

## Cross-Platform Validation

Admin configuration changes should be verified in B2B. After admin tests, run:

```bash
# Verify config changes reflected in B2B
npx playwright test --project=b2b config-validation
```

Key flags to validate cross-platform:

| Admin Config | B2B Effect |
|-------------|------------|
| `anonymousAccess` | Catálogo accessible sin login |
| `anonymousHidePrice` | Precios visibles/ocultos |
| `enablePaymentDocumentsB2B` | Botón facturas visible |
| `enableKhipu` | Opción Khipu en checkout |
| `disableObservationInput` | Campo notas en carrito |
| Banner enabled | Banner visible en header |
| Promotion active | Precio con descuento en catálogo |

